  {
    "hotel_id": "4782362",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hanoi-oriental-pearl-hotel/hotel/hanoi-vn.html",
    "name": "Eco Nest Apartment & Hotel Dinh Ngang",
    "detail": "Just got back from a 5 days 4 nights in Hanoi, where we stayed at the Hanoi Oriental Pearl. Very conveniently located near the Old Quarter and several Embassies (including Canada, and Thailand, in our case). The hotel is very close to the railroad, and rooms with balcony face busy streets, so if you have light sleep and require quietness, you might want to look for something else. However, if you enjoy this busy city's sounds and you can sleep through it, the rooms were very clean (although they show a little age), comfortable, and the service was simply amazing. Everyone in the hotel went out of their way to assist us and share their knowledge about the city. A very cheap but extremely enjoyable stay with the nice staff at Oriental Pearl. Will definitely consider next time we travel to beautiful Hanoi!",
